public interface DirectedEdge
extends Edge

An interface for representing a directed edge between two vertices. This interface can be seen as a refinement of the equals method that takes into account the orientation of the edge.

Method Summary
 boolean equals(Object o)
          Returns true if o connects the same two vertices and have the same edge orientation.
